RULES FOR COMPILING tofHVgui
----------------------------

FIRST:make sure you cvs co PATH_TO_MY_HVGUI_DIRECTORY/MapUtils

First Time Compilation
----------------------- 
(1) make sure that environment variables are properly set up.
    Use the command:
      source /group/clas/builds/PRODUCTION/packages/cms/jlab.cshrc
(2) change to MapUtils dir and type "make"
(3) go to main directory (hvGUI/) and type "make all"

Everytime you change/upgrade your version of ROOT,
libMapUtils.a must be recompiled FIRST linking to the new ROOT libs.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
(1) decend into MapUtils
(2) type "make clean" then rm libMapUtils.a then "make all"

